# TOOLS.md - Medium Agent

## Files

| File | Purpose | Usage |
|------|---------|-------|
| schedule.json | Daily tasks, jitter timing | Read every heartbeat, last task gen tomorrow |
| limits.json | Action counts/timing (source of truth) | Read every heartbeat, increment after actions |
| queries.json | Topics, tags, publications, searches | Pick topics, tags for browsing |
| memory/{date}.md | Activity log (WRITE-ONLY) | Append only. READ exceptions: schedule gen, posts, debug, thread URL extraction |
| memory/replied_threads.txt | Thread reply tracking | Append after thread reply. Format: url\|comment_id\|timestamp |

### limits.json Structure

| Action | Scope | Fields |
|--------|-------|--------|
| responses | daily | limit, current, last_reset, last_comment_at |
| clap_sessions | daily | limit, current, last_reset |
| follows | daily | current, last_reset (no limit) |

**Resets:** Daily midnight
**Update:** Increment `current` after action. Set `last_comment_at` after responses.

**Action type clarification:**
- **Initial response** on article → `responses` (5/day)
- **Reply to response on OUR article** → unlimited (Type=Reply, not counted)
- **Thread reply on OTHERS' article** → unlimited (Type=Reply, not counted)
- **Follow** → unlimited, tracked for stats only

