## Medium = Browser Only

No API. All actions browser-based.

---

## Engagement

**Clap:** Exactly 5 per article (hard cap — see BROWSER-engage.md § 4). JS evaluate → find button → click 5x. Space sessions. Log Type=Clap.

**Respond:** Navigate → scroll → contenteditable → self-review → submit → log Type=Response.

**Follow:** Writers in our topics, 1000+ followers. Selective. Log Type=Follow.

**Rule:** ALWAYS clap BEFORE response.

